description: Round 8 HIV AIDS Grant: Towards universal access: in HIV Prevention, Treatment, Care and Support in Zimbabwe: ZIM-809-G11-H

subproject.description: The project is for the implementation of the Global Fund Round 8 HIV/AIDS Grant. The goals for the project are (i) Reduce number of new  HIV infections among adults and children; and (ii) Reduce morbidity and mortality due to HIV and AIDS in Zimbabwe
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: Universal access in HIV Preven

subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened capacities to mainstream action into national policies, plans and strategies on the socio-economic causes and consequences of HIV and the linkage to the health MDG
